commit_message:
Create hifiasm.sh

Slurm written for genome assembly pipeline ran on TAMUCC HPC

Create salsa.sh

Slurm written for genome assembly pipeline on TAMUCC HPC

Create hic_align.sh

Slurm written for genome assembly pipeline on TAMUCC HPC

Create wtbdg2_assembly.sh

Slurm script designed for use on TAMUCC HPC running genome assembler wtdbg2

Create blast.sh

Slurm written to be executed on TAMUCC HPC to blast red grouper sequences against a mitochondrial genome for potential contaminates

Create remove_mtdna.sh

Slurm written for use on TAMUCC HPC designed to remove any potential mtDNA fragments present in sequences

Create adapter_trim.sh

Slurm designed for use on TAMUCC HPC to remove adapters from PacBio Hifi reads prior to genome assembly

Create jellyfish.sh

Slurm designed for use on TAMUCC HPC to analyze input reads for genome assembly using estimator jellyfish

Create bam2fastx.sh

Slurm designed to be used on TAMUCC HPC converting bams files for genome assembly to fastq files

Merge pull request #1 from klanoue98/klanoue98-patch-1

Create pacbioqc.sh
